HEADWORD: Single-breasted
<hw>Sin"gle-breast`ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Lapping over
the breast only far enough to permit of buttoning, and having buttons on
one edge only; <as>as, a <ex>single-breasted</ex> coast</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

